{"tid":313604,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]短遊花蓮","createTime":"2017-07-08T13:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T17:05:39.000Z","uid":4048,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40bece1c986f56b83109bdadae05ecda40f5f0eb","tid":313604,"uid":4048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:05:37.000Z","msg":"想同大家分享一下最近一次花蓮之旅。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/210409_eb0e19c4ac9f548aed23b85c857c2ad4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F210409_eb0e19c4ac9f548aed23b85c857c2ad4.jpg&h=f5f1337a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到左台北機場先搭捷運去台車站，然後搭台鐵去花蓮。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/210432_d1bb878147d04d511f11ce36e488dd53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F210432_d1bb878147d04d511f11ce36e488dd53.jpg&h=fa696637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於時間好緊迫，其實都好驚搭唔到火車，因為我去到只能趕尾班車，如果趕唔到就。。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好彩最尾都俾我趕到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/210446_ec5ed811542c92bc2e4b7498404ea175.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F210446_ec5ed811542c92bc2e4b7498404ea175.jpg&h=8f354d1d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25b330f8dc25a85b7b2cbb782e5e9a82abe3b4b0","tid":313604,"uid":4048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:07:33.000Z","msg":"去到花蓮已經係凌晨1點幾，所以我到民宿沖完涼都即刻瞓。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992382a278506e276c9fb93346f5cff1a82e4a8e","tid":313604,"uid":4048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:17:52.000Z","msg":"交代返少少野先，我有兩個朋友一早去左台灣玩左兩個星期，所以我今次係去JOIN佢地，係花蓮會合。<br />\n由於佢地係宜蘭識左一個花蓮原住民女仔，所以之後嗰幾日都同佢一齊周圍玩。<br />\n<br />\n第二日，呢個原住民女仔就揸住一架小貨車黎接我地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/211604_5b188b4f7747a5f7c9dd216a215e636d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F211604_5b188b4f7747a5f7c9dd216a215e636d.jpg&h=0e45f8e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/211605_4aa96178270aa90e1fc6da79264022f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F211605_4aa96178270aa90e1fc6da79264022f4.jpg&h=490d42ab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/211608_a176a826f318eddea5ab4b60297ed7f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F211608_a176a826f318eddea5ab4b60297ed7f8.jpg&h=479ee5d1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/211609_08d42f67347bfe843be46ef733aaae6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F211609_08d42f67347bfe843be46ef733aaae6e.jpg&h=2efbecc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐係後面都幾唔舒服其實，不過又係一種體驗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2d41cb70e808104683f3186f3fa965a262cc10","tid":313604,"uid":4048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:56:00.000Z","msg":"介紹返個原住民女仔先，佢叫HARU醬，佢話佢嬷嬷係受日本教育，而且佢係春天出世，所以改左佢個名叫HARU醬。<br />\n<br />\n呢一日係HARU醬同佢屋企人嘅family day，佢地去左一條溪邊玩水同燒野食。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/214106_043818acfcac9de91cd2e4d4b9be7e9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F214106_043818acfcac9de91cd2e4d4b9be7e9d.jpg&h=ddbc0695&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/214107_e17e04549ceeff4fcc4be071281959b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F214107_e17e04549ceeff4fcc4be071281959b0.jpg&h=37c00ee6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/214108_cd7615bd55eebdd8de986b1831ee28ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F214108_cd7615bd55eebdd8de986b1831ee28ec.jpg&h=51da4fa1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/214113_0e961df5e2ec19aa0273d348926d9d2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F214113_0e961df5e2ec19aa0273d348926d9d2b.jpg&h=b43dbfce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/214132_f39216864cf7e24b5c78060fc012f9f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F214132_f39216864cf7e24b5c78060fc012f9f7.jpg&h=9fc45cdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個叫藤壺，生係海邊，佢地係石板上面燒黎食。<br />\n根據我粗淺嘅BIO知識，藤壺係咁多生物中，性器官最長嘅物種（有錯請指正），所以台灣人叫佢做男人加油站。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/214529_95e15aa4523fc1df40f64764a9fd3e68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F214529_95e15aa4523fc1df40f64764a9fd3e68.jpg&h=a8fddc81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n燒熟左之後就係咁，攞塊石扑爛個殻，食面啲肉。<br />\n藤壺嘅肉嘅口感淋淋地，味道有啲似硯肉，都幾新奇有趣。<br />\n<br />\n然後唔少得嘅就係酒。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/214810_dd050f76f37ce2d2281b0dff7e5b977b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F214810_dd050f76f37ce2d2281b0dff7e5b977b.jpg&h=8c92813a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHARU醬嘅屋企人話原住民係中意溝酒飲。（FYR：佢地話台灣共有12族，而佢地嗰一族叫阿美族，歌手蕭敬騰就係屬於阿美族。）<br />\n佢地最中意保力達溝沙士，可以話俾大家知係勁難飲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n附近有個呀伯係度賣雪糕同燒腸仔。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/215518_4043cf57fc69343e639044f7999f9e4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F215518_4043cf57fc69343e639044f7999f9e4f.jpg&h=7c96e693&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/215520_1e71a74255c7be6cd34a09433f0214ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F215520_1e71a74255c7be6cd34a09433f0214ed.jpg&h=3ed0327e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雪糕係佢自己整嘅，食落去有啲似沙冰咁。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e262ea2930a5156542d4c2ec6433ecedac4fc0","tid":313604,"uid":4048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:43:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-QlW9l7Ack0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-QlW9l7Ack0&d=WUtS7zjqaBfPrTqMarLEs10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=a824b4e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-QlW9l7Ack0</a><br />\n之後佢地仲去左玩跳水<br />\n雖然唔知佢地估做乜係度鳩叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n台灣嘅天氣好反覆，玩下玩下就落起大雨黎。<br />\n之後HARU醬就帶左我地返屋企，而我地呢晚就會係HARU醬屋企過夜。<br />\n就係咁，我地就坐住小貸車向HARU醬屋企進發。"},{"pid":"d993d7f0bf751f479754c51e6ab86ad1fea2f291","tid":313604,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:53:44.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"f447fb7b7bf68f0b449216cd5e4e07e7e8c7dfbc","tid":313604,"uid":78913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T10:15:46.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2785d412244c570207c5708b06792851578ea36","tid":313604,"uid":1842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T10:18:09.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"4ab2b6c6c4c0c09fda86954182b6806dcc2f950f","tid":313604,"uid":11144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:03:51.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"52ed3c445e1949fb6e91923291de760d40efbb86","tid":313604,"uid":35867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:05:47.000Z","msg":"快運有正航bor"},{"pid":"fbd07a8b7bb7dc30ae41a266b90767f9f15b2192","tid":313604,"uid":4048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:01:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快運有正航bor</blockquote><br />\n係呀 但係時間唔啱。 我飛嗰日朝早有野做，趕唔到。"},{"pid":"e9a8f7664da3cfe3f5bdbb62b3fb54b3ffc83eb1","tid":313604,"uid":4048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:05:11.000Z","msg":"繼續。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n返到HARU醬屋企，沖左個涼之後，我地就去左食野。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢度就係HARU醬屋企附近。"},{"pid":"193754a62882479559981fd66171fc7b74fe581b","tid":313604,"uid":4048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:09:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>繼續。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n返到HARU醬屋企，沖左個涼之後，我地就去左食野。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢度就係HARU醬屋企附近。</blockquote><br />\n屌禁錯制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n繼續。。。。<br />\n呢度係HARU醬屋企附近。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/210625_f2ff413d84d6e8479314d1f6ecc0817e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F210625_f2ff413d84d6e8479314d1f6ecc0817e.jpg&h=144e5fb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢隻係佢隻狗。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/210657_3fd0417c9b9f96e91509fdfe969dfa0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F210657_3fd0417c9b9f96e91509fdfe969dfa0d.jpg&h=68532886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢叫林書豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHARU醬話佢地一家姓林，養佢嗰時係林書豪最HIT嗰期，所以就改佢個名做林書豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地係附近搵左間野食飯，我就叫左個魯肉飯。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/210930_ea061dc9e46f81ae4ce74864ea04424d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F210930_ea061dc9e46f81ae4ce74864ea04424d.jpg&h=18facbf3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56f25c20a14ac4aeb22472f37d149ebd6da8c53d","tid":313604,"uid":4048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:14:20.000Z","msg":"大家玩完水其實都好攰，我地食完野就返左去HARU醬屋企休息，直到夜晚我地先出去夜市搵食。<br />\n<br />\n我地去左東大門夜市。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/211320_176aff472d191b678ced23ae9e0a3f44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F211320_176aff472d191b678ced23ae9e0a3f44.jpg&h=25a78019&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/211325_b6a6d4526348b6485b58eb47890d39e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F211325_b6a6d4526348b6485b58eb47890d39e9.jpg&h=61602baa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/211332_2d0a12f5f4f3028d060136b81297bf26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F211332_2d0a12f5f4f3028d060136b81297bf26.jpg&h=939917a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/211338_dd6d95a36523a381bbff98c71f70a478.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F211338_dd6d95a36523a381bbff98c71f70a478.jpg&h=622ae711&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/211342_7cc9378be031b7c412777d0e11111cdb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F211342_7cc9378be031b7c412777d0e11111cdb.jpg&h=bb677631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上面嗰個係炸OREO，我話你知，真係唔係咩都可以攞去炸。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019eb456eec1732be81b59e7940800f619a52d2b","tid":313604,"uid":4048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:17:23.000Z","msg":"係夜市入面有原住民嘅表演，大家一齊欣賞下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FzWbvBPe1BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFzWbvBPe1BA&d=WUtS7zjqaBfPrTqMarLEs10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=ea459443\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FzWbvBPe1BA</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有待頭藝人嘅表演。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fqDZuemcUNQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfqDZuemcUNQ&d=WUtS7zjqaBfPrTqMarLEs10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=999f338f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fqDZuemcUNQ</a>"},{"pid":"3749a486679fd14bd32fca50a47c135f9bf5f740","tid":313604,"uid":4048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:30:24.000Z","msg":"夜市大家都去得多，所以我唔多講。<br />\n<br />\n然後第二日我地同HARU醬就打算一齊去露營。<br />\n今次露營哤地點叫「四八高地」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/212415_a552ace696fdea26334b6b0cdf553d02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F212415_a552ace696fdea26334b6b0cdf553d02.jpg&h=292e9f96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/212422_c70f9add019c074727de9947ead3d54e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F212422_c70f9add019c074727de9947ead3d54e.jpg&h=e1b3acab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/212429_344a6897c37fefca022840cfd1780721.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F212429_344a6897c37fefca022840cfd1780721.jpg&h=52b01eac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高地隔離係一個軍營，嗰日佢地係隔離應該練緊射擊，係咁啪啪啪。<br />\n<br />\n你地䏲，幾多台灣MK仔MK妹上黎影相。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/212745_063d052d1f314db01b7f29aecfd5699f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F212745_063d052d1f314db01b7f29aecfd5699f.jpg&h=36fef77e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/0